OL,3,CYou can see the latest edition of
OL,4,CAround The House here:
OL,6,F'A generation in genuine distress' -
OL,7,Fthat's how the former Health Secretary
OL,8,FAlan Milburn has described the cohort
OL,9,Fof 16-24 year olds currently not in
OL,10,Feducation, training or employment. His
OL,11,Ffirst report on Young People and Work
OL,12,Fhas put the plight of more than a
OL,13,Fmillion young people at the heart of
OL,14,Fthe political debate. Recommendations
OL,15,Ffor action will follow in the Autumn,
OL,16,Fbut his assessment is clear: the
OL,17,Fproblem of being Not in Education,
OL,18,FEmployment of Training (NEET) is
OL,19,Fgrounded in social disadvantage.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
