OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1780758677
OL,3,CYou can see the latest edition of
OL,4,CAround The House here:
OL,6,FTom Sheldrick's panel consider how
OL,7,Fmore jobs and training can be
OL,8,Fprovided, the toll of unemployment on
OL,9,Fyoung people's mental health - and why
OL,10,Fsociety urgently needs to help them
OL,11,Finto the workplace:
OL,13,FAlso in the programme - the PM under
OL,14,Fpressure with rivals circling for the
OL,15,FLabour leadership, and ten years after
OL,16,Fthe upheaval of the Brexit referendum,
OL,17,FTom's guests reflect on what leaving
OL,18,Fthe EU has meant for our region and
OL,19,Fwhat sort of relationship we need with
OL,20,FEurope now.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
